item.title: Finishing Kylie's CO 14ers
item.description: An awesome 2-day adventure completing Kylie's final Colorado 14er! Technical traverse between peaks, dramatic rockfall events, and an unforgettable celebration at 14,350 feet. This route has real rockfall potential and requires group coordination, but offers incredible rewards for experienced climbers.
